{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDisposeFunction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dispose"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceDisposeFunc","text":"GSourceDisposeFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" function will be called once the reference count of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"reaches zero but before any of the state of the source is freed, especially"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before the finalize function (set as part of the [type","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncs","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"]) is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This means that at this point "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is still a valid [struct"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and it is allow for the reference count to increase again until ","type":"text"},{"code":"dispose","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"returns.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The dispose function can be used to clear any ‘weak